LINE.Text: Dubai has undergone a remarkable economic transformation over the past
40 years. The construction and expansion of ports Rashid and Jebel Ali has
been a crucial driver of the emirate's and the region's growth
Number of vessels calling in to
Jebel Ali's vast network reaches all comers of
the globe running 90 weekly services to move
